---
title: Char Siu Pork Belly & Stir-Fried Greens with Garlic Rice & Peanuts
description: What’s an instant way to bring bold, international flavours to pork? Add this sweet ‘n’ salty char siu sauce to melt-in-your-mouth
pork belly. Teamed with sticky veggies, plus an aromatic garlic rice, this meal will make your taste buds sing!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6753cb797668eda5b411105b-bbe29e37.jpeg
